<th width="550" style="padding: 5px; background-color: #dd0000"><strong style="color: #ffffff;">Concert/Expo AD'HOC - Samedi 15 Mai 2010 - Epinay sur Orge</strong></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="550" style="padding: 10px; background-color: #cccccc;">
<p><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://www.adhocmusic.com/age5331.php"><img src="http://www.adhocmusic.com/img/get.php/172/244/ffffff/agenda/5331" width="172" height="244" border="0" align="right" style="margin: 5px;" alt="" /></a></p>
<p>Les groupes au programme seront :</p>
<ul>
<li><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://www.adhocmusic.com/furykane"><strong>FURYKANE</strong></a> (Rock Fusion)</li>
